Feline2::

She looked at HotRod with a lost in thought expression on her face. 
"I..I remember you meaning something to me. But I don't remember 
exactly what it was." She was looking into his eyes, searching for 
answers. "What was I to you?"

> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> He felt her touch. Something was wrong. She didn't have the emotion 
of
> love. Then the truth hit him. She had forgotten what they had.
> He took her hands in his.
> "You dont remember 'us' do you?"
